metadata.name: In Memoriam: The Spy Balloon
metadata.description:
In Memoriam: The Spy Balloon

We mourn the loss of a brave and daring spy balloon, shot down by a F-22 in the line of duty. You served your country with distinction, providing valuable intelligence to your leaders. Your passing marks the end of an era, and you will be remembered as a symbol of the unwavering commitment and dedication of the spy community.

You will be missed by all who knew you, and we offer our condolences to your family, friends, and fellow spies. May you rest in peace, knowing that your service to your country will never be forgotten.
